<section id="TechInfo.XEN">
 <title>Xen Limits</title>
 <para>Since &sles; 11 SP2, we removed the 32-bit hypervisor as a
 virtualization host. 32-bit virtual guests are not affected and are
 fully supported with the provided 64-bit hypervisor.</para>
