 <para>
  In Xen 4.4, the hypervisor bundled with &sles; 12, Dom0 is
  able to see and handle a maximum of 512 logical CPUs. The hypervisor
  itself, however, can access up to logical 256 logical CPUs and schedule
  those for the VMs.
 </para>
